query:
SELECT DISTINCT t.codigo, t.cursos, t.instituicoes, e.tipoEvento
FROM turmas t
INNER JOIN eventos e ON e.turmaId = t.id
WHERE e.dataInicio IS NOT NULL
LIMIT 10
